mpop: mpop (POP3 client)
mpop:
mpop: mpop is a small and fast POP3 client. Features include mail filtering,
mpop: delivery to mbox files, maildir folders or a mail delivery agent, a
mpop: very fast POP3 implementation, many authentication methods, good
mpop: TLS/SSL support, IPv6 support, and more.
mpop:
mpop: Homepage: http://mpop.sourceforge.net/
mpop:
